2025-09-12 07:13:52 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:13:52 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 07:13:52 [INFO] Can continue: Hello there.
2025-09-12 07:13:52 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:13:53 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:13:53 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:13:53 [INFO] Can continue: You, you're the human that killed Tyras. Arianwyn told<br>us about you.
2025-09-12 07:13:53 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:13:54 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:13:54 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 07:13:54 [INFO] Can continue: That's me. Could you take me to Arianwyn?
2025-09-12 07:13:54 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:13:54 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:13:54 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:13:54 [INFO] Can continue: Why should we? All you humans do is take and destroy<br>with no care for others. We don't need your help.<br>You've done enough damage.
2025-09-12 07:13:54 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:13:56 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:13:56 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 07:13:56 [INFO] Can continue: Well I admit that I've made a few mistakes, but my<br>intentions were good, I swear.
2025-09-12 07:13:56 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:13:56 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:13:56 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:13:56 [INFO] Can continue: Maybe, but it's not a risk worth taking. It was the acts<br>of humans that led to my grandmother's death. You will<br>bring similar ruin to us.
2025-09-12 07:13:56 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:13:57 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:13:57 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 07:13:57 [INFO] Can continue: Your grandmother?
2025-09-12 07:13:57 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:13:58 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:13:58 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:13:58 [INFO] Can continue: Glarial, wife to King Baxtorian. At one time my<br>grandparents ruled over a great elven kingdom. But<br>your kind put an end to that.
2025-09-12 07:13:58 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:13:59 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:13:59 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 07:13:59 [INFO] Can continue: Glarial? I know that name, I visited her tomb. I moved<br>her remains to Baxtorian Falls, I thought that was<br>where she would want to be.
2025-09-12 07:13:59 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:13:59 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:13:59 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:13:59 [INFO] Can continue: You... you moved her into the waterfall? That... that's<br>the perfect place for her to be.
2025-09-12 07:13:59 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:14:00 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:14:00 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 07:14:00 [INFO] Can continue: Maybe this human isn't as bad as you think Islwyn.
2025-09-12 07:14:00 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:14:00 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:14:00 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:14:00 [INFO] Can continue: Maybe...
2025-09-12 07:14:00 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:14:01 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:14:01 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:14:01 [INFO] Can continue: Very well human, we will take you to Arianwyn. But<br>first, there is something you must do. If my<br>grandmother has been moved, then her new tomb must<br>be consecrated. Do this, and you will earn my trust.
2025-09-12 07:14:01 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:14:02 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:14:02 [INFO] ===
2025-09-12 07:14:02 [INFO] Yes.
2025-09-12 07:14:02 [INFO] No.
2025-09-12 07:14:02 [INFO] ===
2025-09-12 07:14:02 [INFO] 918 Option: 1 Yes.
