2025-09-12 07:14:03 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:14:03 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 07:14:03 [INFO] Can continue: Deal, what do I need to do?
2025-09-12 07:14:03 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:14:04 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:14:04 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:14:04 [INFO] Can continue: I don't know the consecration process myself. You<br>should speak with Eluned. She is wise in the ways of the<br>ritual.
2025-09-12 07:14:04 [INFO] Continue
