2025-09-12 07:14:07 [INFO] Interacting Eluned Talk-to
2025-09-12 07:14:09 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:14:09 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 07:14:09 [INFO] Can continue: Hey there, Islwyn said you might be able to help me.<br>He told me you'd know how to consecrate ground for<br>an elven burial. I need to consecrate Glarial's new<br>resting place.
2025-09-12 07:14:09 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:14:10 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:14:10 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 07:14:10 [INFO] Can continue: That I do. It is elvish tradition to plant a specially<br>enchanted crystal seed at the graves of our ancestors.<br>The seed will create guardians to protect the area.
2025-09-12 07:14:10 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:14:11 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:14:11 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 07:14:11 [INFO] Can continue: Unfortunately, the crystal seed must be tuned to the<br>person it's protecting, a new seed won't do. But you<br>should be able to recover the seed from her old tomb.
2025-09-12 07:14:11 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:14:11 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:14:11 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 07:14:11 [INFO] Can continue: I'm not very familiar with the lands to the east so I<br>couldn't tell you where her old tomb is I'm afraid.
2025-09-12 07:14:11 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:14:12 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:14:12 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 07:14:12 [INFO] Can continue: That's okay, I've been there before. It's just south east<br>of Baxtorian Falls.
2025-09-12 07:14:12 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:14:13 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:14:13 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 07:14:13 [INFO] Can continue: Excellent. Now, the tomb's guardians will be protecting<br>the seed, you'll need to defeat one of them to get it.<br>Once you have it, return to me and I will re-enchant<br>it.
2025-09-12 07:14:13 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:14:14 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:14:14 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 07:14:14 [INFO] Can continue: Okay, I'll be back as soon as I have it.
