2025-09-12 07:24:10 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:24:10 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 07:24:10 [INFO] Can continue: Hello Islwyn.
2025-09-12 07:24:10 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:24:11 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:24:11 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:24:11 [INFO] Can continue: You have returned! Is it done?
2025-09-12 07:24:11 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:24:12 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:24:12 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 07:24:12 [INFO] Can continue: It is, your grandmother's resting place has been<br>consecrated.
2025-09-12 07:24:12 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:24:13 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:24:13 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:24:13 [INFO] Can continue: Thank you, I admit I was wrong about you. You have<br>showed care and compassion that I didn't think possible<br>for a human. As promised, we will take you to<br>Arianwyn. But first, a reward for you.
2025-09-12 07:24:13 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:24:14 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:24:14 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn shows you a crystal bow and a crystal shield.
2025-09-12 07:24:14 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:24:15 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:24:15 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:24:15 [INFO] Can continue: We elves use equipment formed out of crystal itself, far<br>superior to your human weapons. However, the crystal<br>does degrade with use and will eventually revert to<br>seed.
2025-09-12 07:24:15 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:24:16 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:24:16 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:24:16 [INFO] Can continue: Both the shield and the bow I am carrying have been<br>used, so are not at their full potential. They should still<br>be quite useful though.
2025-09-12 07:24:16 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:24:17 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:24:17 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 07:24:17 [INFO] Can continue: Fascinating. What do you mean by 'revert to seed'?
2025-09-12 07:24:17 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:24:19 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:24:19 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:24:19 [INFO] Can continue: All elven crystal starts as a seed. It can then be sung<br>into various shapes through the power of the voice.<br>Eventually, it reverts back to seed, ready for the next<br>song.
2025-09-12 07:24:19 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:24:19 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:24:19 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:24:19 [INFO] Can continue: Keep an eye out for an elf named Ilfeen as you<br>wander the forest. She can chant crystal seeds into new<br>items for you.
2025-09-12 07:24:19 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:24:20 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:24:20 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 07:24:20 [INFO] Can continue: I will, thanks.
2025-09-12 07:24:20 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:24:21 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:24:21 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 07:24:21 [INFO] Can continue: Anyway, I'm sure you will learn more about crystal<br>seeds as you spend time with our kind. For now<br>though, which one of these creations would you like?
2025-09-12 07:24:21 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:24:22 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:24:22 [INFO] ===
2025-09-12 07:24:22 [INFO] Shields are for wimps! Give me the bow!
2025-09-12 07:24:22 [INFO] I don't like running and hiding behind mushrooms. Shield please!
2025-09-12 07:24:22 [INFO] I need some time to decide.
2025-09-12 07:24:22 [INFO] ===
2025-09-12 07:24:22 [INFO] 918 Option: 2 I don't like running and hiding behind mushrooms. Shield please!
2025-09-12 07:24:23 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 07:24:23 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 07:24:23 [INFO] Can continue: I don't like running and hiding behind mushrooms.<br>Shield please!
2025-09-12 07:24:23 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 07:24:25 [INFO] Solving dialogue
