2025-09-12 08:11:25 [INFO] Can continue: It was a worthy deed.
2025-09-12 08:11:25 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 08:11:26 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 08:11:26 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 08:11:26 [INFO] Can continue: Indeed it was. Anyway, are you ready to be taken to<br>Arianwyn?
2025-09-12 08:11:26 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 08:11:27 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 08:11:27 [INFO] ===
