2025-09-12 08:11:29 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 08:11:29 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 08:11:29 [INFO] Can continue: I'm ready.
2025-09-12 08:11:29 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 08:11:32 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 08:11:32 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 08:11:32 [INFO] Can continue: Very well. Arianwyn will be in Lletya, I can take you<br>there.
